    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/6f25246bd1fc840f346e06852abc581f.webp?t=1707847939\" width=617 height=59 /></span><br>《Atrio》是一款灵感源于赛博朋克的末日后生存游戏。通过捕捉和利用生物与环境，让大自然为你服务，不惜一切代价帮助你生存。你即将面临的许多威胁和挑战都很难独自应对。你必须建造、自动化并优化你的系统，与世界互相牵制才能生存下去。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/8c7833cdd47b173eccd77b7e2aefa1e7.webp?t=1707847939\" width=611 height=18 /></span><br>建造庞大高效的自动化系统，让基地在你探索世界的同时维持运转。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/ed77bdc6d25a1b02d8cba2d8f6ba5672.poster.avif?t=1707847939\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/ed77bdc6d25a1b02d8cba2d8f6ba5672.webm?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/ed77bdc6d25a1b02d8cba2d8f6ba5672.mp4?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/ca7db3f0e3b57e7609914f10deb97cd3.webp?t=1707847939\" width=611 height=18 /></span><br>深入野外猎捕生物。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/8cec8a3aa69d764f2d3d313a163db827.poster.avif?t=1707847939\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/8cec8a3aa69d764f2d3d313a163db827.webm?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/8cec8a3aa69d764f2d3d313a163db827.mp4?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每一只被捕获的生物都在你的装配线上扮演着独特的角色。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/0cdce90e40fe6f23d87df6ab61eaf37f.poster.avif?t=1707847939\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/0cdce90e40fe6f23d87df6ab61eaf37f.webm?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/0cdce90e40fe6f23d87df6ab61eaf37f.mp4?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/7cf18391716876bd3a3c33678d1c1011.webp?t=1707847939\" width=611 height=19 /></span><br>你是一台没有名字的人形机器人，负责恢复3号站点的运转。人类都去哪儿了？你真正的目的是什么？这些巨大的雕像是什么？深入黑暗的野外是找到答案的唯一途径。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/174f13a27278dca0d9122380a75289f6.poster.avif?t=1707847939\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/174f13a27278dca0d9122380a75289f6.webm?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/174f13a27278dca0d9122380a75289f6.mp4?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2> <strong>手工打造的开放世界</strong>：探索一个美丽而独特的世界，感受耀眼霓虹灯与黑暗的鲜明对比，竭尽全力将灯光打开。 <br><strong>诙谐的故事</strong>：在诙谐的故事剧情中了解你被送到地面的真正原因。<br><strong>沙盒模式</strong>：只想轻松游戏？沙盒模式让你可以在自己的安全模拟环境下尽情发挥创意。<br><strong>独特的生物</strong>：各色稀奇古怪的半机械半有机生物在野外等待着你。<br><strong>拉屎的小鹿？</strong>：没错！鹿粪这种非同寻常的宝贝可能是你生存下去的关键所在。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >评论</h2> <i>“这是有史以来最伟大的游戏”</i>——来自某人（但愿很快会出现）……游戏还没有发布，所以我们（目前）没得到任何评论！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于我们</h2> 《Disjoint》的制作者！我们是一支来自加拿大的三人小组，热爱生存与自动化游戏。<br>斯蒂芬曾是微软的项目经理，后来转职成为游戏设计师；凯尔曾是奥运会空中技巧运动员；弗朗西斯目前的胡须从耳朵到底端已有2英尺（再长15英尺6英寸就能打破世界纪录了）！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开放开发</h2> 你可以通过YouTube上的每月视频日志随时了解《Atrio》的动态。快来看看开发团队正在做什么，然后在游戏中给出反馈。我们开放抢先体验的目标就是倾听你们的想法，并邀请你参与我们正在进行的工作。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/6cd61375c47b8a2915d6a92f773b47ae.poster.avif?t=1707847939\" width=616 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/6cd61375c47b8a2915d6a92f773b47ae.webm?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125390/extras/6cd61375c47b8a2915d6a92f773b47ae.mp4?t=1707847939\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
